15 WHEREAS, on Addiction Recovery Awareness Day and throughout the year, we recommit
16 ourselves to helping Georgians who are seeking the treatment they need and we celebrate
17 Georgians who are embracing a life of recovery.
18 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES that
19 the members of this body recognize January 21, 2025, as Addiction Recovery Awareness
20 Day in the State of Georgia.
21 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Clerk of the House of Representatives is authorized
22 and directed to make appropriate copies of this resolution available for distribution to the
23 public and the press.
